item.title: Jessie James Decker to Make Acting Debut With ‘The Christmas Ring’ (Exclusive)
item.description: Kelsey Grammer, Benjamin Hollingsworth and Jana Kramer also star in the holiday film that adapts author Karen Kingsbury’s new book and hits theaters this fall.
